Version 2.1.1 (25/6/2026)
* Reworked the app in Kotlin and Jetpack Compose
* Updated Android, Gradle, and library versions
+ Added RLE seed pattern support
+ Added random grid generation and a random startup background
* Improved settings persistence and save-to-file handling
* Fixed canvas sizing, drawer gestures, and row/column handling

Version 2.0.1
* Fix minor issues

